,Recommended,658620,34670786,Posted: 1 September,all,末原 恭子,"I was busy so I haven't really gotten to play this game a lot, but today, I finally managed to get the time to finish 1 route.Before anything else, this game is a visual novel, this means there's nudity inside and if you downloded the uncensored patch it's a really wholesome experience! The uncensored patch is not only free, it's also official so it won't cause you problems! Down below is the patch.https://www.jastusa.com/wonderful-everydayFirst~ gameplay.If you're new to the visual novel genre you would probably ask 'why is this a game?' Because for you, games might include shooting stuff, slashing stuff, hiding from stuff, or to be more general, actually moving and controlling stuff. That's not what happens in the genre of 'Visual Novels'. Here it's like reading a book while listening to err an audio book. The only gameplay that you will get is the time when the game asks you to make a decision on who do you want to do something with (that something can either be: kiss, bone, grope, date, whatever).Second~ Plot.Subarashiki Hibi contains 6 stories. This my friends is just first of six, Down The Rabbit Hole. The protagonist is Yuki Minakami a girl who encounters another girl named Zakuro Takashima, someone who likes throwing stuffed animals/ dolls off a rooftop. You also have a childhood friend Kagami Wakatsuki and Tsukasa Wakatsuki. Beyakuwoz you are the peak of masculinity, despite being a girl, the three of the girls (especially the sisters) seems to have an interest in your non-existent peenees, When Zakuro decides to volunteer to be your maid and live with you, this conflicts with the sisters' who also want a share of your sexy sexy butt so they decided 'fak you ♥♥♥♥♥ we're living here too!' And basically that's where it begins, 4 girls living together with 1 girl in constant threat of losing her virginity every time she's alone with 1 of them. From there you can choose if you want to have a relationship with them or pursue the legend of the 'girl of the sky'. I chose to play it safe for my first playthrough and gave my virginity to the twintailed girl. All jokes aside, this has a very intriguing plot! It starts out slow, but once you get into it, it's very easy to get hooked! Before I knew it I couldn't turn the game off! I finished one playthrough but after I write this review I'm immediately hopping on to the next!Third~ Characters!The characters are great and very memorable! You will always have a reason to choose one over the other because each of them has a personality! Unlike in other game where you can replace characters with a wet towel and I wouldn't give a fak and not notice it, the characters for this game are adorable, lovable and you can really sympathize with them.Fourth~ Art!Art is amazing! Everyone is beautiful! The CGs and the nudity are extremely nice! My only complain is that I wish they could've used something like Live 2d to animate the characters while they're talking. But, even without that, the game still has beautiful girls drawn beautifully and that's already a lot!Fifth~ Voice Acting!The voice acting here is purrrrrrfecccctt! It's just perfect! You can tell the personalities of each character just from their voices! That's a good sign that the voice actors really did their job well! Then, when it comes to the good part (if you know what i mean), they really sound their part and if you close your eyes, you can really imagine them 'getting it on'.Sixth~ translations!After the horrible, ♥♥♥♥♥♥ translations of Dark Elf, Les Fleursword and The Heiress, I'm proud to say that it's nice to see good translation for once. I'm doing it a disservice just to call it good actually. It's ♥♥♥♥ing amazing! They didn't fall to the trap of using machine translations, they really worked hard for this game to be translated and they deserve all my praise for that!Overall I really liked this game and I recommend this to everyone! Unless you hate the Visual Novel genre or just dont like Yuri to begin with, then this game is a must buy!Okay now let's review something else. god damn it steam, this is an adult game and you're heartifying words such as 'D I C K',  and ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ for its review?"
